# Band 8 Sample Answer

## Introduction

The bar chart compares the proportions of weekly household income spent on eight different categories by families in one country in 1968 and 2018.

**翻译：**
该柱状图比较了某国居民家庭在1968年和2018年将每周收入用于八种不同类别支出的比例。

---

## Overview

Overall, the proportion of income spent on food declined dramatically over the fifty-year period, while expenditure on housing, transport and leisure increased considerably. In addition, spending on fuel and power, clothing and footwear, and personal goods all became less significant in 2018 compared with 1968.

**翻译：**
总体来看，在这五十年间，家庭用于食品的支出比例大幅下降，而住房、交通和休闲方面的支出则显著增加。此外，燃料与能源、服装与鞋类以及个人用品的支出在2018年相比1968年都变得不那么重要。

---

## Body Paragraph 1

In 1968, food accounted for by far the largest proportion of weekly household expenditure, at approximately 35%. However, this figure fell sharply to around 17% in 2018. By contrast, spending on leisure more than doubled, rising from roughly 9% to over 20%, making it the largest category in 2018. Housing expenditure also increased noticeably, climbing from about 10% to nearly 19% over the same period.

**翻译：**
1968年，食品支出占家庭每周支出的比例最高，约为35%。然而，到2018年，这一数字大幅下降至约17%。相比之下，休闲支出增长超过两倍，从大约9%上升至20%以上，并成为2018年占比最大的支出类别。住房支出也明显增加，从约10%上升至接近19%。

---

## Body Paragraph 2

A similar upward trend can be seen in transport spending, which rose from around 8% in 1968 to approximately 14% in 2018. Meanwhile, expenditure on clothing and footwear halved from about 10% to 5%. Spending on fuel and power declined slightly, from roughly 6% to 4%, while the proportion allocated to personal goods decreased from around 8% to just 4%. Household goods remained relatively stable overall, accounting for about 7% in both years.

**翻译：**
交通支出也呈现类似的上升趋势，从1968年的约8%增长至2018年的约14%。与此同时，服装和鞋类支出则减半，从约10%下降至5%。燃料与能源支出略有下降，从大约6%降至4%；个人用品支出也从约8%下降到仅4%。相比之下，家庭用品支出总体较为稳定，两年都约占7%。

---

# ⭐ 这篇 Band 8 的关键写法

## ✅ 1. Overview 不只是“升降”

真正高分 overview：

不是：

❌ some categories increased while others decreased

而是：

✅ 点出：

* 最大变化
* 主要趋势
* 最显著类别

比如：

> food declined dramatically
> leisure became the largest category

这就是：

# “抓主线”

---

# ⭐ 这篇里的高级表达（直接背）

## 描述“占最大比例”

> accounted for by far the largest proportion

Task 1 超级高级表达。

以后：

* spending
* population
* exports
* energy

全能套。

---

## 描述“大幅下降”

> fell sharply

> declined dramatically

比：

❌ went down a lot

高级太多。

---

## 描述“翻倍”

> more than doubled

雅思特别喜欢这个表达。

---

# ⭐ 这篇的高分逻辑

## 1968 的核心：

# Food 最大

## 2018 的核心：

# Leisure + Housing 上升

所以文章核心逻辑是：

# 👉 “家庭消费结构发生变化”

这才是 Task 1 真正要写的东西。

不是：

# ❌ 念数字

而是：

# ✅ “总结社会消费趋势”

